New Delhi, the 15th November 1962.
The undersigned is directed to state that, with effect from
the afternoon of Novem ber 15, 1962, Shri Jai Sukh Lal Hathi has
relinquished the office of Minister of Labour in the Ministry of
La bour & Employment and has assumed the office of Minister of Supply
in the Ministry of Economic and Defence Co-ordination.
The undersigned is also directed to state that, with effect
from the afternoon of November 15, 1962, the desi gnation of
Shri Mehr Chand Khanna will be Minister of Works, Housing &
Rehabilitation,
(B. G. Rau)
Joint Secretary to the Cabinet.
